data.description: Let's ring in the New Year by reducing the price on this home by   $25,000.00 from original price of $420,000.00    Don't just wait for any old property.....live the dream in this perfect home in a serene and quiet area.    This makes it a great  opportunity for you to own a 2020 built Clayton Manufactured home on 5 open wonderful acres.  Clayton Homes are one of the best in the entire industry.  Presently there are 2 horses who call this paradise home.  Wide open space allows for additional dreams to come true.  Of the 5 acres - 3 acres are newly fenced.  Once you step into the home you will be struck with the openness and beautiful beamed ceilings as well as the warm and cozy fireplace, perfect for the occasional cold nights in the wintertime.   To your immediate left you will find a built in coat hanging station with extra storage.  To your right you'll feast your eyes on a "TO DIE FOR KITCHEN" Impressive  staggered kitchen cabinets give you much more than just enough space to hold all your exceptional kitchen ware and an island big enough to host at least 4 or 5 friends while you cook on your cooktop and prepare a meal or two for family and other guests.  Easy to  move freely about with a window above the kitchen sink that lets in the natural light as well as allows you to gaze outside.  The Master Bedroom leaves nothing to be desired..... You will have no problem accommodating large furniture.  The additional 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms are on the other  side of the house which allows for plenty of privacy.  Laundry room has a slop sink and back door leading outside.  Owners have upgraded the Air Conditioning Unit to 500 SIRS and also upgraded the water treatment system to the finest.  One of the best things about Morriston is you are just right smack in the middle of Ocala and Dunnellon.  Quite and peaceful surroundings yet close enough to shopping and entertainment. This home must be seen  in order to get the full benefit of what a great deal this really is.    Give  me a call for an appointment
